						<br><span class="hotelname">Crowne Plaza Times Square Manhattan, NY</span><br><img alt="red line" height="1" src="owshare/crowneplaza/worldwide/images/red.gif" vspace="7" width="270"><br><b>Crowne Plaza Times Square Manhattan<br><GEO TYPE="US">1605 Broadway<br>New York<br>NY 10019 <br>USA</GEO><br>Toll-free: (USA only) +1 800 243 6969</b><br><b>Tel: +1 212 977 4000</b><br><b>Fax: +1 212 333 7393</b><br><b>E-mail: <a href="mailto:info@cpmny.com">info@cpmny.com</a><br></b><img alt="red line" height="1" src="owshare/crowneplaza/worldwide/images/red.gif" vspace="7" width="270"><br>Whether visiting New York for business or pleasure, the 46-story Crowne Plaza Times Square Manhattan offers the best in service and value.  Located in the heart of the Theater District, it is the perfect place; take in a Broadway show, shop on Fifth Avenue, stroll in Central Park or wander to the city's numerous landmarks and attractions.  Our 770 guest rooms and suites all provide spectacular views of the Manhattan skyline.  Rated by the Zagat Guide as &#147;the friendliest hotel in New York City&#148;, our staff looks forward to making your stay truly memorable.
<br /><br />
Our brand has spent a great deal of time researching and implementing our <strong>Sleep Advantage Program</strong>.  We put our resources into creating a better place to sleep by enlisting the expertise of Dr. Michael Breus, Ph.D.  Our program is a holistic approach to a better night's sleep, which includes: Comfortable New Beds, Quiet Zones, Sleep CD and Relaxation Tips, Sleep Amenities, and Guaranteed Wake-Up Call.
<br /><br />
Our flexible meeting and banquet facilities are perfect for any occasion, from 7 to 700. Crowne Plaza Times Square is the <strong>Place To Meet</strong> and provides Meeting Success with its 2-hour response time to all sales leads and a proposal by the next day; a <strong>Crowne Meetings Director</strong> to assist you with your meeting from the time of planning to the time you leave; and a daily debrief by the <strong>Crowne Meetings Director</strong> to provide a complete itemization of all accounting for that day's expenditures.
<br /><br />
Samplings Restaurant and the Lobby Bar offer a wide selection of food and drinks from dawn until dusk, whether you&rsquo;re looking for a cup of Starbuck&rsquo;s coffee or tea with a light snack, a full dinner, cocktails or a glass from our range of wines. In-room dining is available. Take care of your fitness needs with our extensive health and leisure facilities, including Manhattan's largest indoor swimming pool. We also offer full Concierge services, on-site valet parking, Business Center services, and a tour and travel desk.
<br /><br />
Crowne Plaza has over 100 hotels in the Americas, all of which offer upscale amenities in a comfortable and elegant environment, helping you get your work done or simply relax while away from home.  
<br /><br />
The Crowne Plaza Times Square Manhattan is owned by K G  Land and operated by InterContinental Hotels Group, Inc.<br />
